---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Bell Type Furnace Components For Bright Annealing" description="You deserve superior sealing technology to ensure the perfect bright finish. Our bell furnace accessories provide the highest level of atmospheric integrity.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Furnace Application Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Bell Type Furnace Components For Bright Annealing</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>You deserve superior sealing technology to ensure the perfect bright finish during your annealing and tempering processes. Our bell furnace accessories are designed to provide the highest level of atmospheric integrity for both heating and cooling stages. You can achieve better surface quality and prevent decarburization on your metal coils or parts by relying on our industrial-grade furnace consumables and precision feeding systems.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Technical Challenge</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Bell furnaces require perfect air-tight sealing during long heating cycles. Oxidation leads to surface discoloration and costly finishing work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Weigu Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Weigu provides high-performance furnace base seals and protective atmosphere probes. You achieve a consistent bright finish on every load, reducing scrap.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Components For This Application</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> High-Vacuum Seals</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Atmosphere Probes</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Base Gaskets</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Thermal Shields</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <CTA title="Optimize Your Bell Furnace Process Today" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
